{"tid":765272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國熱到瀝青都溶 各地驚現「神秘古蹟」？","createTime":"2018-08-02T15:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T05:12:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"19f8340daf40513f35100dcafbcda8ac832c5590","tid":765272,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180802/20467046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F20467046&d=CDQTrxGF9a3eRILCDEPtX0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b814f4b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F20467046&h=90a6a84c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180802/20467046</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月02日 <br />\n<br />\n英國熱到瀝青都溶<br />\n各地驚現「神秘古蹟」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國受自1976年以來最長的一次熱浪侵襲，雨水不足，截至7月16日降雨量僅得47毫米，是1961年以來最乾旱，英國的衞星相片因而「變色」，全國更有多處古蹟「現形」。<br />\n<br />\n從相片看到，5月的衞星相片顯示英國仍是綠油油一片，綠草如茵；但7月的衞星相片卻變成啡色，意味英國受熱浪及乾旱夾擊後，土地變得乾涸，看來猶如沙漠一樣。<br />\n<br />\n熱浪亦令德文郡（Devon）一個水庫水位下降，露出被水淹沒近一世紀的村莊；遍布全國各地的考古遺址亦因水位下降而逐一「現形」。<br />\n<br />\n蘭開夏郡（Lancashire）一處1940年代的花園本已荒廢，熱浪卻令當年花園輪廓再現；諾福克郡（Norfolk）一片草地亦出現舊的農作物印記，看起來有如幾何圖形的圖騰紋理。<br />\n<br />\n另有人上載伯明翰（Birmingham）一張田園相片，不少人指原本茂綠的田園，頓變成猶如美國中西部的乾旱田地，「我來自英國，住在美國，我可以確認這相信就像(美國)中西部的農田」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美法院禁3D打印槍圖則放上網<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【今日笑一笑】小貓遇着雞　裝兇作勢定投降？"},{"pid":"7122fd4023b6a718fc902bd4238db8f915fbdf0a","tid":765272,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T22:54:28.000Z","msg":"其實英國所謂熱浪同香港夏天差唔多<br />\n<br />\n只不過英國無冷氣"},{"pid":"5a28099ed76e345b87b4c3cdb2dde94c832b6fb0","tid":765272,"uid":132038,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:04:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d411334e10e3ed4b592a7f162176921a0980e7ff","tid":765272,"uid":11686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7122fd4023b6a718fc902bd4238db8f915fbdf0a","tid":765272,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T22:54:28.000Z","msg":"其實英國所謂熱浪同香港夏天差唔多<br />\n<br />\n只不過英國無冷氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:06:26.000Z","msg":"成40度喎"},{"pid":"1449609704c8ac8b1b56bf9d9119729c2d2a06da","tid":765272,"uid":17510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d411334e10e3ed4b592a7f162176921a0980e7ff","tid":765272,"uid":11686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7122fd4023b6a718fc902bd4238db8f915fbdf0a","tid":765272,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T22:54:28.000Z","msg":"其實英國所謂熱浪同香港夏天差唔多<br />\n<br />\n只不過英國無冷氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:06:26.000Z","msg":"成40度喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:24:44.000Z","msg":"我果到應該感覺上無去到40度<br />\n無check溫度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過學上面講句<br />\n可能真係因為英國夠乾燥得黎又成日都有風吹住<br />\n所以唔會學得太熱仲幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3630ca849fae27615e4fee7a6b5942c69586af0e","tid":765272,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:29:31.000Z","msg":"瀝青都熱到溶啦<br />\n仲吹到香港濕熱世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6797598bb12e61b029a2977b3800ffd8939772","tid":765272,"uid":67653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3630ca849fae27615e4fee7a6b5942c69586af0e","tid":765272,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:29:31.000Z","msg":"瀝青都熱到溶啦<br />\n仲吹到香港濕熱世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:32:42.000Z","msg":"體感溫度同實際溫度<br />\n<br />\n瀝青唔會排汗散熱，人會"},{"pid":"2dc8bbd3b830e34a741eb27a44ac2e22d763bb7e","tid":765272,"uid":11686,"lik